Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:20.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:29.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:40.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:09.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:16.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:27.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:30.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:41.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:49.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:02:00.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:02.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:15.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:20.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:22.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:29.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:39.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:43.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the \NGreat Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way \Nto the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the \NGrand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After being separated \Nfrom his friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy comes to the rescue his brother \NAce who has been captured by the Navy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by sneaking into Impel Down - \Nthe greatest prison in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He heard from some prisoners that Ace \Nwould most likely be held on level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and ran into an \Nunexpected acquaintance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll change my plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now for some chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Break through the Crimson Hell! \NBuggy's Chaos-Inducing Plan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop \NEmergency Escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fall and have \Nyour head crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aerial Tailspin Big Top!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How d'you like that, \Nyou sea gorilla?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No damage at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't! Stop punching me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've gotten \Nstronger since we last met!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're tough! What \Nkind of animal are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're fighters from the sea called \NBlue Gorilla known as Blugori!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay sharp! There're \Nstill 4 more...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then! I see you've \Ntaken care of them already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have time to \Nmess around with these!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! He kicked a \Nlot of Blugori ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey you! Who are you?!\N--Let us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought there was \Nonly one escapee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there's just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could be wrong \Nbut I saw two guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, 5 Blugoris have been beaten \Nin front of community cell #10!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5 of them? It can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any prisoners on level 1 \Nwho stand a chance against Blugoris!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna rescue Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one \Nwho's screaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey guys? The key? Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Keep \Nyour mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Unlike you, your \Nbrother was very polite...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really a time \Nto be partying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you attack Luffy if you \Ndon't even know where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a \Nspoilsport, Alvida!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us enjoy ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna see Luffy? \NI know where he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? He knows \Nwhere Luffy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! Excuse me for \Ninterrupting your banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was drawn here by the \Nsmell of all this good food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ace. \NNice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no no, you don't have to be that \Npolite. The pleasure is all ours...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:08:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about your \Nname! Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Captain, \Nhe's the "Fire Fist"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fire Fist" Ace! Whitebeard's \NSecond Division Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You know my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we hit it off and \Nbecame drinking buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I feel very sorry about \Nwhat happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the foolishness of the Navy \Nto mess with Whitebeard's crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna get to level 5. \NThat's where Ace is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! Go by yourself! \NI'm no friend of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to that \Nhell hole! See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not willing to \Nescape, I'll do it on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's 10 or more navy ships out \Nthere. Are you sure you can make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 or more?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:09:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it! They must be \Npreparing for Whitebeard's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now isn't the best time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just kill some time and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, I'll just ask \Nsomebody else!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No no, it can't be!\NIt's stupid to even think it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then, good \Nluck with your escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What're you...\N--There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Up there!\N--They found me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you yell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, that's a beautiful \Narmlet! Can I have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you so interested all of the \Nsudden?! This was a gift from Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you where Ace is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! If you give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, in that case!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, first, let's \Nlose our enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold onto my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drop those, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how Buggy the Clown's \NChop-Chop power works!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can chop apart his body and \Ncontrol each part as he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the pieces are controllable\Nonly in a limited area and to use his power,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his feet must be on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! How lucky I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that I found the treasure \NI was looking for in hell like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really \Nsure that this is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the cave \Nwhere Captain John
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who acted so cruelly to \Nprotect his treasure hid them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is! Proceed carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, where there are treasures, \Nthere are usually traps or guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One false move \Nand you're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there will be \Nsome kind of monster
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or bloody traps like \Nyou'd see in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's continue with \Nthe tunnel construction!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You guys must \Nbe the new crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Boss, I love this job!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! All our sweat turns into a part of \Nthe tunnel that will make people smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And beer tastes so much \Nbetter after hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of this \Ngoody-goody laborer crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We kept sailing here and there in the Grand \NLine looking for the treasure after that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we couldn't \Nfind it anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To top it all, I was caught in a navy \Npost while I walked in by mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was shut up \Nin this prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my luck has \Nnot run out yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run as fast as you \Ncan, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lead you to the \Nentrance of level 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Level 2? Aren't you listening? \NI wanna go to level 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Straw Hat! You'll be \Nunable to go straight to level 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Impel Down, this first \Nbasement is what they call level 1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.68,0:12:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and as you go down to \Nlevel 2, level 3 and so on,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you encounter more vicious \Ncriminals who have been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only ever been to level \N4 to be tortured by fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't know about \Nthe floors below.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But level 5 holds the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,extraordinary criminals with bounties \Nof hundreds of millions or more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard from some prisoners \Nthat there are more floors below!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that there are heinous \Nmonsters whose existences
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have been deleted from history!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a rumor but maybe \Nthat's where Ace is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I can only \Nlead you to level 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Suddenly you're \Nnot such a bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, because you said \Nyou'll give me the armlet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that will tell me where \NCaptain John's treasure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I shouldn't have \Nopened my big mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a pretty crappy pirate \Nto have been caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He wasn't even paying attention! \NThank god he's such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that this armlet \Nfunctions as a treasure map!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no clue at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were paying attention! \NDamn! Then I have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then, you \Ncan have it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that it's a treasure map \Nbut you're still gonna give it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Rescuing Ace is \Nmore important to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't you think that I may just take \Noff with it if you give it to me now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Because you gave your \Nword that you'd lead me to Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me with \Nthose trusting eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a sly and worthless man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:15:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't \Nbelieve a guy like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally have Captain John's \Ntreasure mark after all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, how the hell \Ndo I get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Is it faster to break \Nthrough the wall? I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how Luffy's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I warned him not to \Nget into any trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They built this place as a \Nfort that locks people in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once they catch you, you'll \Nnever be able to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you're strong
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but promise me that you \Nwon't get in any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so \Nmuch, Hancock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hancock... \NHancock ...ncock...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Luffy! I can hear your \Nheavenly voice in my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's about time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm! What a \Npleasant scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:17:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like jailers \Ndoing pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you like it, \NHancock-dono?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you didn't hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one more \Nchance so please do enjoy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about screams! I can't hear \Nthe voice in my heart because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I did wrong \Nbut she's stepping on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? I'm a vice warden!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that, Hancock-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm kinda enjoying this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops! Did I say \Nthat out loud?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Buggy the \NClown who escaped...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who is the other one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the jailers' room!\NThen we shouldn't go this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Straw Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?\NA forest in the prison?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a crimson forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're prisoners!\NThis is not just a forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaves are as sharp as blade \Nbecause they're Blade Trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The grass is actually needles \Nwhich prick  your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called Spike Needle Grass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chased by loosed venomous \Nspiders and jailers,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,prisoners run around the forest
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get cut by leaves and \Ngrasses which shed their blood
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,causing them to agonize!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is level 1 - \Nthe Crimson Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:19:02.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)}"The Underwater Prison - Impel Down - Level 1\NCrimson Hell"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.79,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:02.99,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a real hell! Is this the kind \Nof thing they're doing to Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Let's just keep falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! We're gonna get cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna get cut! \NJust shut up and hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! My feet! Throw \Nthem to the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Augh! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I get my feet on the \Nground, it's a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to use stairs \Nto go down from this floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need a key to \Nopen the door to the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered that there's a way to \Nescape the agony of the Crimson Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a way out of hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's as dark as night!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the way out but nobody \Nwants to escape from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know \Nwhy, Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this hole is \Nconnected to level 2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is an even \Nmore terrifying hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There may be people who try to \Nescape from hell back to earth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there aren't people stupid \Nenough to descend deeper into hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is good for us! \NWe can just jump down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah but down below, \Nthere's... No, wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's deep! I wonder \Nwhat's down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! What a hotfoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:21:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't afraid of anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at least now he can't \Nstop me if I just take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm free! I finally got the treasure \Nmark that I always dreamed of!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find your own way! \NGood-bye, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Down to level 3 or level 4 - it doesn't \Nmatter either way you're a goner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Blugori! You can't chop \Nme because I ate Chop-Chop fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You got to \Nbe kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:22:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surveillance Room! \NThere is another guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.77,0:22:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just fell down to level 2!\NCan you look for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.02,0:22:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:28.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,900)}"The Underwater Prison - Impel Down - Level 2\NFloor of Wild Beasts From Hell"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:24.60,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.60,0:22:26.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The beasts unusually agitated!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:29.45,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they hungry or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.22,0:22:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no energy \Nleft to be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.29,0:22:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way we're \Ngonna be their dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,0:23:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Buggy fall down to level 2,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.70,0:23:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where beasts of fearsome strength roam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the floor of the wild beasts of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Hancock reaches \Nthe heart of the prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.41,0:23:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where she encounters Warden Magellan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Strongest Man in the Prison!\NPoison Man Magellan Appears!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
